==============================================================================
QUICKSTART GUIDE
==============================================================================
Setup and run Linear Utility:
   I. Linearity Utility:
   Run linearity utility
      I. HID device
      # sudo LinearAp  /dev/usb/hiddevx n
      II. RS232 device
      # sudo LinearAp  /dev/ttySx n
      where x=0,1,2...n, n = 4 or 9 <default>

